Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um… you’re very good at singing, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my dream is to become a singe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
