Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m completely tone-deaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, listen—{idk if em dash is good here or not}{WAIT, DO I DETECT SOME NAVI IN THIS LINE}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao!
