Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll be right back. Wait for me, okay?{GARGHABARGLE}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:36.04,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,“Masao-san{\fsp-3}”{\fsp}. So he {\i0}is{\i1} a gu{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.{she puts the "san" in there w}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m coming right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s me! Me!
