Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eat properl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao-san, I made a boxed lunch for you.{My brain refuses to let me leave this line with "bento" in it}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.{PIMP STUD PLAYER}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m really looking forward to your next live show!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ll come again late{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao-san, um, I hope this isn’t a bothe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, but…{THIS FUCKING MUSIC}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Farewell!{SUCH A ROMATIC WORD}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actuall{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, I don’t really know them very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they really appreciate my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also want to hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right, one of them said she was looking forward to hearing you pla{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you perform?
