Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’ve even thought about returning to the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but with the support of my fans, I can still eat regularl{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I figured, what the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Usually when I feel like singing, it’s already nighttime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.57,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That ghostly voice was him all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I’m Ichinokura Masao. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m Yamada Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your song, that is.{yeah…, he definitely says うた and not うたう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I’ll see you late{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.68,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It’s good, you know. Your song, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:59.19,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,If I practice a lot, I wonder if I’ll ever be able to sing like him.
