Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu! Asu! It’s that voice again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s all right, Onee-chan. Listen carefull{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:20.80,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,Glittering, sparkling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:24.36,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,basking in the rays of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:28.04,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
