Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:36.97,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,a memory of summe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.86,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The voice is singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s a really pretty voice.{lolol}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.20,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I wish I had noticed this soone{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.{BUTTRAEP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:37.66,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,It’s a reall{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, really beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, good evening. Was I disturbing you?{blargh}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all, it was a wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evening. I’m Asu’s older siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, Yamada Kyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like it’s gotten colde{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like that’s all I’ve got for toda{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.41,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I need get home and practice singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.04,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I’ll be able to sing like Ichinokura-san one da{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.86,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I suppose that’s not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it’s Ichinokura-san.
