Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s probably impossible, so it’s okay if you decline.{biasduibasdouiasd. I AM A PROFESSINAL TRANSLATOER AND I PROABABLY MISTRNASLATED THIS LINE HORRIBL}
