Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}. I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s all right! I still have my siste{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, if there’s ever anything I can help with, please ask.
