Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oka{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, leave it to me. I’ll sing for you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:13.60,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Even though he promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:18.46,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,He promised that he’d sing for me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His song… I can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:32.32,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,Flowing easily along,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:35.46,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,the wind whispers b{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.16,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:45.72,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In the radiant fields of green,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.18,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,let’s invite—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His song…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao-san!{jesus fucking christ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Masao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?{NO ENDING SENTENCES IN PREPOSITIONS}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masao-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was spending nights at my part time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems I caused you some undue worr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.{blargh}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, make sure to tell us beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorr{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone loves Ichinokura-san, don’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being turned down at all my auditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started thinking that becoming a\Nmusician might be impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to give up singing for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I {\i1}do{\i0} want to keep on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s why I got a part time job, so I could afford to reclaim my guita{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His guita{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}…{lul}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A promise that I would sing for you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:28.22,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,Flowing easily along,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:31.22,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,the wind whispers b{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:35.08,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:41.66,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In the radiant fields of green,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.76,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,let’s invite the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.98,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:54.84,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,Glittering, sparkling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.94,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,basking in the rays of sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:01.76,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:08.12,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,A rustling heart is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.17,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,a memory of summe{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:14.70,INSERT SONGS 5000,,0,0,0,,In that wa{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.05,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:32.13,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s what I can do. The only thing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.05,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Music is mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.81,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,With the ebb and flow of each note,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.80,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I can feel my spirits rising.{yeah so what I destroyed the parallels between the opening and the closing WHAT YOU GONNA DO ABOUT IT}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:47.08,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s why I will keep on singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:01.35,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,That’s why I want to stay here foreve{\fsp-1}r{\fsp}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.71,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I’ll try my best with Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:11.15,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,So we will always be able to hear the music.
